This template displays a "Template documentation" box like you are seeing now.

It is primarily used by {{tl|template doc}} to automatically display the documentation for the template from a /doc subpage, but can also be used to display inline documentation.

==Usage==
 '''{{tlx|template doc inline|1&#61;''inline documentation''|2&#61;''pagename''}}'''

* ''Inline documentation'' is the text to display inside the box.
* ''Pagename'' refers to the name of the documentation page, which if specified, creates [view] and [edit] boxes to the right of the heading.

